  <section class="ofs-section ofs-section-alt compact-panel">
    <div class="ofs-copy">
      <p class="kicker">Security and privacy controls</p>
      <h2>Local protection with clear settings</h2>
      <p>Offline FileSecure uses a vault PIN, optional biometric unlock, screen protection setting, auto-lock, and visible encryption details. The Vault PIN controls access to the app, while vault files themselves are stored encrypted.</p>
      <p>The vault model is local and offline: protected files are not uploaded to DK App Tools, and there is no account, no cloud upload, no ads, and no tracking. Google Play may be used to check for and install app updates.</p>
      <p>DK App Tools cannot remotely recover vault files for you.</p>
    </div>
